---
// Classmates section component
---

<section class="blog" id="classmates">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>CLASSMATES</h2>
      <p>Stay connected with your classmates - Join our email list for reunion updates and class news.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Join Our Mailing List</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="blog-grid">
      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-image">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4c7a9c_6dc2372241a54033b682aaa5057503ea~mv2.png" alt="Classmate profile" />
        </div>
        <div class="blog-content">
          <h3>Mike Thompson</h3>
          <p>Now a successful software engineer in Seattle, Mike remembers being the captain of the debate team and winning state championships.</p>
          <a href="#" class="blog-link">View Profile</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-image">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4c7a9c_6dc2372241a54033b682aaa5057503ea~mv2.png" alt="Classmate profile" />
        </div>
        <div class="blog-content">
          <h3>Jennifer Martinez</h3>
          <p>Jennifer is now a pediatrician in Omaha and a mother of three. She was our valedictorian and student body president.</p>
          <a href="#" class="blog-link">View Profile</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-image">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4c7a9c_6dc2372241a54033b682aaa5057503ea~mv2.png" alt="Classmate profile" />
        </div>
        <div class="blog-content">
          <h3>David Chen</h3>
          <p>David owns a successful restaurant chain in Lincoln and is excited to share his culinary journey since graduation.</p>
          <a href="#" class="blog-link">View Profile</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
    
    <div class="shop-section">
      <div class="shop-content">
        <h2>reunion merchandise</h2>
        <p>T-SHIRTS, TOTES BAGS, PINS, HATS, STICKERS, YEARBOOKS</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">ORDER MERCHANDISE</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blog {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 42px;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  
  .section-header p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  
  .blog-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  
  .blog-image {
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .blog-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .blog-content {
    padding: 30px;
  }
  
  .blog-content h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  
  .blog-content p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  
  .blog-link {
    color: #1e40af;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .blog-link:hover {
    color: #1e3a8b;
  }
  
  .shop-section {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  .shop-content h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }
  
  .shop-content p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  
  .btn {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid #1e40af;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #1e3a8b;
    border-color: #1e3a8b;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    
    .shop-content h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
